high_descs: Turn completely around to face sink, walk toward sink, turn left, walk to tub.
Take right hand washcloth out of the tub.
Turn right, walk to sink, turn left to face sink.
Put washcloth in sink, fill sink, drain sink, take cloth out.
Turn right, walk to counter, turn right, walk to tub
Put cloth in tub to left of the other washcloth.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned washcloth in the tub.

high_descs: Turn right and walk up to the bathtub
Pick up the right most pink rag from the bathtub
Turn around and walk up to the sink
Wash the rag under water in the sink then remove it
Turn around and walk up to the bathtub
Put the rag in the bathtub
anns.task_desc: Put the cleaned rag in the bathtub

high_descs: Turn and go to the bathtub.
Pick up a dirty rag in the bathtub.
Turn and go to the sink.
Wash the dirty rag in the sink.
Turn and go to the bathtub.
Put the rag in the bathtub.
anns.task_desc: Clean a dirty rag in the bathtub.
